data.description: Beautiful true log cabin home nestled in the woods of Paupacken Lake Estates.  This home is ready for you to move in.  Owner has purchased new washer and dryer along with new gas stove and kitchen has granite counter tops.  All appliances are included with the sale of the property.  There is on-demand hot water heater that supplies immediate hot water.  The hook-up for a gas stove has already been installed. Spend every summer relaxing on your beautiful front porch enjoying nature or spend every day year round enjoying the serene snow falls and abundance of wildlife that surrounds this stunning log cabin., Baths: 1 Bath Lev 1,Full Bath - Master,1 Bath Lev 2, Beds: 2+ Bed 1st,1 Bed 2nd, SqFt Fin - Main: 865.00, SqFt Fin - 3rd: 0.00, Tax Information: Available, Modern Kitchen: Y, SqFt Fin - 2nd: 485.00
